{"tid":539521,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[打手慎入]咩係山頭文化? 點解TVB話要汪阿姐減少山頭文化?","createTime":"2018-01-24T15:23:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-28T03:39:55.000Z","uid":66822,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9da41b7d4383c8c4009ed9d138530897cc845ad5","tid":539521,"uid":66822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T15:23:20.000Z","msg":"真話唔講得，如果要講&hellip;除非真係好有輩份。<br />\n<br />\n汪明荃噚晚就把握住大台頒獎禮呢個機會，代表全公司領獎時講咗一番感受，包括叫大台加人工、關心下員工、同埋少啲山頭文化！此話一出，證明都汪阿姐幾有地位，對比番，連出爐視帝王浩信今日出活動，都話唔明咩叫山頭文化，你就知汪阿姐有幾勁。<br />\n阿姐呢番說話，引嚟好多網民喺社交網洗版讚好：<br />\n汪阿姐唔怕你雪佢，梗係敢講真話；<br />\n無論阿姐之前係點，佢呢時呢刻都仲肯為後輩出聲呀；<br />\n無求就膽大；<br />\n亞姐講得中肯，撑妳；<br />\n《蘋果》今日聯絡到阿姐，佢話：「我都收到好多同事短訊，呢個問題（山頭文化）其實好多公司都有，既然o依家老闆咁有心想做好電視發展，希望公司好好珍惜人材，我都係講咗好多人想講嘅說話啫。」問到佢講山頭係指邊啲高層，阿姐就話：「呢啲我就唔評論啦。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180122/57740865\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180122%2F57740865&d=w1QEDnFPI8RY27QzDYX3YcPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=e8b71bbc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180122%2F57740865&h=7938592a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180122/57740865</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n山頭文化即係咩? 成篇新聞都冇解釋到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19a488daf8800c2f34b23b81379296ff9da95bbd","tid":539521,"uid":152047,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T15:37:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://lmgtfy.com/?q=%E5%B1%B1%E9%A0%AD%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flmgtfy.com%2F%3Fq%3D%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E6%2596%2587%25E5%258C%2596&d=w1QEDnFPI8RY27QzDYX3YcPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=d8099e06\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lmgtfy.com/?q=%E5%B1%B1%E9%A0%AD%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96</a>"},{"pid":"0c32b7